Description:
    The command 'rails g shiny:plugin plugins/[name]' creates a skeleton
    for developing a ShinyCMS plugin

Example:
    cd ShinyCMS
    rails g shiny:plugin plugins/ShinyThing

    This generates a skeletal ShinyCMS plugin in ShinyCMS/plugins/ShinyThing

    Please read Plugins.md in the ShinyCMS developer docs for more information
